SpoonerPlacements.Note: This is no ordinary comedown. Sure, the bright, pulsing lights are there, tapering off to the familiar, migraine-inducing point. But the usual sense of complete disorientation is accompanied by spine-crushing momentum, and your hands are holding some kind of wheel. Yep, there's only one conclusion: you're coming to your senses on a point-to-point stunt race for the Rocket Voltic. Good luck - you'll need it.
